<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Latencies Creating, Updating and Terminating Environments>
We are investigating increased latencies creating, updating and terminating environments in the AP-SOUTHEAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Latencies Creating, Updating and Terminating Environments>
We continue to investigate increased latencies creating, updating and terminating Elastic Beanstalk environments in the AP-SOUTHEAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Latencies Creating, Updating and Terminating Environments>
Between 4:04 AM and 5:54 AM PST some customers experienced elevated latencies creating, updating and terminating environments in the AP-SOUTHEAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
